1. *Carstvo* je bio zlatno doba srpske istorije. (The *empire* was the golden age of Serbian history.)
2. Naša kompanija je lider u *carstvu* IT industrije. (Our company is a leader in the *realm* of the IT industry.)
3. Kao kraljica, ona je vladala *carstvom* sa snagom i mudrošću. (As a queen, she ruled the *empire* with strength and wisdom.)
4. Zemlja je bila podijeljena na više manjih *carstava*. (The country was divided into several smaller *empires*.)
5. Njegova želja za moći bila je nezasitna, želio je vladati *carstvom* pod svaku cijenu. (His desire for power was insatiable, he wanted to rule the *empire* at any cost.)